trans-unit.source: Decodes the given variant Tensor and returns a RaggedTensor. The input could be a scalar, meaning it encodes a single RaggedTensor with ragged_rank output_ragged_rank. It could also have an arbitrary rank, in which case each element is decoded into a RaggedTensor with ragged_rank input_ragged_rank and these are then stacked according to the input shape to output a single RaggedTensor with ragged_rank output_ragged_rank. Each variant element in the input Tensor is decoded by retrieving from the element a 1-D variant Tensor with input_ragged_rank + 1 Tensors, corresponding to the splits and values of the decoded RaggedTensor. If input_ragged_rank is -1, then it is inferred as output_ragged_rank - rank(encoded_ragged). See RaggedTensorToVariant for the corresponding encoding logic.
trans-unit.target: 解码给定的 variant Tensor并返回 RaggedTensor 。所述输入可以是标量，这意味着它编码单个 RaggedTensor 与ragged_rank output_ragged_rank 。它也可以具有任意的等级，在这种情况下，每个元件被解码成 RaggedTensor 与ragged_rank input_ragged_rank ，然后将这些被根据输入形状来输出单个堆叠 RaggedTensor 与ragged_rank output_ragged_rank 。输入Tensor中的每个 variant 元素都可以通过从元素中获取具有 input_ragged_rank + 1 的一维 variant Tensor进行解码张量，对应于解码后的 RaggedTensor 的分割和值。如果 input_ragged_rank 为-1，则将其推断为 output_ragged_rank - rank(encoded_ragged) 。有关相应的编码逻辑，请参见 RaggedTensorToVariant 。
